    "body": "```javascript \r\nconst InfiniteHits = ({ hits, hasMore, refine }) => {\r\n  return <FlatList\r\n    data={hits}\r\n    keyExtractor={item => item.objectID}\r\n    onEndReached={() => refine()}\r\n    renderItem={({ item }) => (\r\n      <CardItem hit={item} />      \r\n    )}\r\n  />\r\n}\r\nexport const ConnectedHits = connectInfiniteHits(InfiniteHits);\r\n```\r\n\r\nin my case refine didn't work ? the function exists but not updating the results",
